  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2612720/extras/cc44694ae4c4104860969efe7b78e0a6.avif?t=1730759129\" width=800 height=200 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >This is a <strong>Small Game</strong> that was originally cranked out in less than one week! Showing what enough effort can do!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >This is a <strong>2D platformer game</strong> with some puzzle elements. And <strong>Secrets...</strong> You have to complete 10 levels to win the game!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >This is also a <strong>Small Preview</strong> before the release of the real Mayhem's World. This is game was made by one person, and I have no prior coding experience beside the slow development of <strong>Mayhem's World!</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >I hope you have fun with my little game!</p>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2612720/extras/cc44694ae4c4104860969efe7b78e0a6.avif?t=1730759129\" width=800 height=200 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >This is a <strong>Small Game</strong> that was originally cranked out in less than one week! Showing what enough effort can do!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >This is a <strong>2D platformer game</strong> with some puzzle elements. And <strong>Secrets...</strong> You have to complete 10 levels to win the game!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >This is also a <strong>Small Preview</strong> before the release of the real Mayhem's World. This is game was made by one person, and I have no prior coding experience beside the slow development of <strong>Mayhem's World!</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >I hope you have fun with my little game!</p>",
